@startuml
title Login Authentication Sequence Diagram

autonumber

actor User

participant "Angular Frontend" as Angular
participant "Auth Component" as UI
participant "FastAPI\nAuth API" as API
participant "Authentication\nService" as Service
participant "User Repository" as Repo
database "SQLite Database" as DB
participant "JWT Service" as JWT

User -> Angular : Open Login Page
Angular -> UI : Display Login Form

User -> UI : Enter Username & Password
UI -> API : POST /api/auth/login\n(username, password)

API -> Service : authenticateUser()

Service -> Repo : findUser(username)

Repo -> DB : SELECT user
DB --> Repo : User Record

Repo --> Service : User Details

Service -> Service : Verify Password

alt Invalid Credentials

Service --> API : Authentication Failed
API --> UI : 401 Unauthorized
UI --> User : Invalid Username/Password

else Valid Credentials

Service -> JWT : Generate JWT Token
JWT --> Service : Access Token

Service --> API : Login Success

API --> UI : 200 OK\nJWT Token + User Info

UI -> UI : Store JWT Token\n(Session Storage)

UI -> API : GET /api/auth/me\nAuthorization: Bearer Token

API -> Service : Validate Token

Service -> JWT : Verify JWT
JWT --> Service : Token Valid

Service -> Repo : Load User Profile

Repo -> DB : SELECT Profile

DB --> Repo : Employee Data

Repo --> Service
Service --> API

API --> UI : User Profile

UI --> Angular : Navigate to Dashboard

Angular --> User : Dashboard Loaded

end

@enduml